{"tid":1639133,"cid":38,"subCid":0,"title":"國際台已開，但問題在於推廣同成效","createTime":"2019-10-08T13:58:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T14:10:55.000Z","uid":225916,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"81cc1cb13c37841eb70f0d522753ac2176a542c0","tid":1639133,"uid":225916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T13:58:34.000Z","msg":"連仔，我好多謝你開咗個國際台<br />\n但問題係 到底應該點樣推廣<br />\n如果唔係開咗都冇人用 咁開咗同冇開冇分別<br />\n都只係香港人圍內，變咗用英文用其他文溝通<br />\n<br />\n設立國際台專用帳號<br />\n只限使用國際台<br />\n<br />\n問題就係到底開ac嘅限制<br />\n我認為使用邀請制會比較好<br />\n一個連登ac可以邀幾個人入 最好有設限<br />\n咁廣大嘅連登仔又可以周圍搵啲對香港有興趣嘅外國人<br />\n(我建議嗰啲帳號可以選定國籍,或者語言,咁會比較好分)"},{"pid":"6d2e28fbcffe217bc1b7bc8cfd1975c3c95937b9","tid":1639133,"uid":243366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T13:59:44.000Z","msg":"Use #AskLIHKG to ask us anything!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1638764\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1638764</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0e4c2b9fabcc59be9d9d0df76e3c646e30a7ce86","tid":1639133,"uid":225916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d2e28fbcffe217bc1b7bc8cfd1975c3c95937b9","tid":1639133,"uid":243366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T13:59:44.000Z","msg":"Use #AskLIHKG to ask us anything!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1638764\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1638764</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T14:01:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幾好<br />\n但好似好麻煩<br />\n長遠都唔對路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f9456a861a929cedd53a9f74ae9843b46151229","tid":1639133,"uid":243366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e4c2b9fabcc59be9d9d0df76e3c646e30a7ce86","tid":1639133,"uid":225916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d2e28fbcffe217bc1b7bc8cfd1975c3c95937b9","tid":1639133,"uid":243366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2